    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《秘密政府》为一款以秘密结社为主角的全球战略游戏。在这款游戏中，您并不会像国王一样治理国家，而会化身为国王背后的推手。您将领导您的兄弟会，将整个世界玩弄在您的股掌之上。游戏的核心内容为操纵权力。兄弟会不会直接下达命令，而是会教唆各个国家，让他们做兄弟会想要做的事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/c007c3f157cb81504d617b962dcca051.webp?t=1760104825\" width=331 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《秘密政府》为一款全球战略游戏，游戏主角为几百年来一直在暗处谨慎地统治人类社会的秘密结社。您并不会领导某个特定的国家，而会领导您的兄弟会，将整个世界玩弄在您的股掌之上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5fb5c2357bce2943c5a37badefa33149.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5fb5c2357bce2943c5a37badefa33149.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5fb5c2357bce2943c5a37badefa33149.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/44eda93dd2f5358760c893c7a4e18a18.webp?t=1760104825\" width=326 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兄弟会的终极目标是建立新的世界秩序。游戏开始时，您会选择您身为宗师的目标，选择将世界改造成怎样的面貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/9403572eb576b776fd156ac8978639a3.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/9403572eb576b776fd156ac8978639a3.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/9403572eb576b776fd156ac8978639a3.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5047d813af3d39f6a1d280a4850ef86a.webp?t=1760104825\" width=327 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您需要派遣特工前往各个国家，想办法拉拢公务员，渗透到权力机构之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/93a5cf3e9f65fd79677e463153682f07.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/93a5cf3e9f65fd79677e463153682f07.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/93a5cf3e9f65fd79677e463153682f07.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/57d2d47a533f596f2043cee66951991c.webp?t=1760104825\" width=327 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过各种各样的手段来操纵一个或多个国家。您可以改变国家的执政势力、意识形态、各个阶层的福祉，或是推动国家发动战争或停止战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/37f02f916a49b0f3c89b15fb2a0d2d20.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/37f02f916a49b0f3c89b15fb2a0d2d20.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/37f02f916a49b0f3c89b15fb2a0d2d20.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/04165c2298d32ddeb80252a069d3e09f.webp?t=1760104825\" width=329 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位导师都有独一无二的特性与能力。您可以选择发展哪项特性，选择特性的发展方式，为特定的任务选择最适合的修士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cd759285aa892a875e01fa2e0e347974.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cd759285aa892a875e01fa2e0e347974.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cd759285aa892a875e01fa2e0e347974.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/37bb0d152c4151337d03a86fb2b56ee1.webp?t=1760104825\" width=326 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了你的兄弟会之外，另一个全球性的兄弟会也想以他们的方式来改变世界。这个兄弟会也同样会拉拢政府成员，操纵国家。你经常会碰到穿着红袍的修士，不过不要急于攻击他们。在某些场合下，他们的行动会对您带来有利的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/dc7931ae5c8165d5a802a108707564bd.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/dc7931ae5c8165d5a802a108707564bd.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/dc7931ae5c8165d5a802a108707564bd.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5157809b3fef23bf3a972b43e01f4d6c.webp?t=1760104825\" width=326 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行动时务必要保持谨慎，否则成员的身份会被政府或其他兄弟会的成员识破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5a7e1ec42bba8f9386654360a6bcc7b7.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5a7e1ec42bba8f9386654360a6bcc7b7.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/5a7e1ec42bba8f9386654360a6bcc7b7.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/19c5a7f0ebf84591f924224f70028f9c.webp?t=1760104825\" width=291 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本游戏中，您并不能直接攻击国家，但您可以挑起各国之间的战争，或是让他们偃旗息鼓，结成同盟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/70035e70da6213338d28d875c46cde8f.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/70035e70da6213338d28d875c46cde8f.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/70035e70da6213338d28d875c46cde8f.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/2baebaee052f0df38b17a5db4f31dcb4.webp?t=1760104825\" width=291 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人民的福祉与国家的富裕程度取决于国家经济。您可以影响各个阶层与不同产业的生产与资源消耗，影响国家之间的贸易状况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/1509315178c4fb7a850e3d99b3dbccb9.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/1509315178c4fb7a850e3d99b3dbccb9.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/1509315178c4fb7a850e3d99b3dbccb9.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/4ec501116d1ef432fdbffc01d1c4b79f.webp?t=1760104825\" width=290 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国家与人民非常相似。两者都会通过阶层进行划分。不同阶层的人们在社会上有各自的角色、价值与需求。人们会不断出生、死亡、迁移，还会从一个阶层跳到另一个阶层。只要您能影响人们，就能影响整个国家，改变该国家在整个世界的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/753850440218745afc8e83ed625bc1fd.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/753850440218745afc8e83ed625bc1fd.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/753850440218745afc8e83ed625bc1fd.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/7f0cf89b01c842a798fa4cfcc2403f35.webp?t=1760104825\" width=327 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本游戏中，一切都是有相互联系的。比如，如果用来生产武器的钢铁短缺，则该国家的战斗力会受到影响。如果您想要扩充军队来提高战斗力，则需要动员农户参军。一旦农户数量减少，粮食的生产量也会降低，从而影响到其他行业。这可能会导致工匠或其他阶级消失、迁移。工匠会在各个产业中工作，生产用来出口的奢侈品，用以补贴国库。因此，您所做的每个决定，都会引发一连串的结果。若想成为优秀的宗师，就必须保持平衡，考虑所有可能的联系，将世界朝着正确的方向推动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/0d159dd1c261d96d18cd7ed1f37e3e31.webp?t=1760104825\" width=290 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您并不仅仅是操控一个国家，而是将整个世界玩弄于股掌之上。游戏中共有两个历史时期可供选择，分别是1685年和1775年。这些年间的政治事件与领土划分也会各自不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/7e21d921cdb5136b35f73372da27de75.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/7e21d921cdb5136b35f73372da27de75.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/7e21d921cdb5136b35f73372da27de75.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/0818ee19bf461f9934f83fbca6c30a8b.webp?t=1760104825\" width=291 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您还没准备好在自由游戏中建立新的秩序，您可以尝试在战役模式中扮演宗师的角色。目前本游戏包含两个战役：英格兰的光荣革命，以及新世界十三个殖民地之间的斗争。在每个战役中，您都需要插手这一时期的主要冲突，使世界朝着与实际历史的方向发展，或是以您自己的方式来改变历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cb7f887b566c558a014fbc095ea6e60d.poster.avif?t=1760104825\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cb7f887b566c558a014fbc095ea6e60d.webm?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946990/extras/cb7f887b566c558a014fbc095ea6e60d.mp4?t=1760104825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >您可以在游戏中执行狡猾的计划</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您并不仅仅是操控一个国家，而是将整个世界玩弄于股掌之上。确定各个国家在新世界的角色，渗透到国家的政府之中，改变国家的法律。让各个国家像提线木偶一样履行您的意志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >间接影响各个国家</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个国家的行动取决于该国通过的法律、执政势力的意识形态、政府形态，以及军事、公共与经济政策。改变这些因素，便可以改变国家的行为。</p>",
